<HEADLINE> CORRECTS to change slug  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
    	   ALBANY, N.Y. (AP) - The winning numbers selected Wednesday in the New
York's "Lotto" drawing were:
<P>
	    Lotto
</P>
<P>
	   51, 46, 10, 45, 9, 5. The supplementary was 3.
</P>
<P>
	   (Fifty-one, forty-six, ten, forty-five, nine, five and supplementary three.)
</P>
